Guidelime.registerGuide(
[[
[N20-21 Stonetalon Mountains]
[GA Horde]
[D A guide created by T H A C E N#9446\\Based on Joana's Speed Leveling guide www.joanasworld.com]
01) Run west into Stonetalon Mountains. When you get there take the path (starting at [G82,98]).
02) Go to the witch doctor in the small cave and turn in "[QT1060 Letter to Jin'Zil]" ([G75,98]).\\Accept "[QA1058 Jin'Zil's Forest Magic]".
03) At the other side of the village, accept "[QA6461 Blood Feeders]" ([G71,95]).
04) Go NW to the Wanted Poster: Besseleth and accept "[QA6284 Arachnophobia]" ([G59,76]).
05) Follow the path west to Sishir Canyon and start working on "[QC1069 Deepmoss Spider Eggs]" and do part of "[QC6461 Blood Feeders]": \\start looting the Deepmoss Eggs and kill 10 Deepmoss Creepers (the Deepmoss Venomspitters does not need to be completed now).
06) GROUP 2+ Players: West in Sishir Canyon do "[QC6284 Arachnophobia]" (Elite): kill/loot Besseleth (lvl 21 elite orange spider, with several possible spawn locations, around [G52,74], /target ).\\NOTE: Besseleth can be soloed later in the guide at level 24 by all classes.
07) Go north to Windshear Crag and turn in "[QT1483 Ziz Fizziks]" at the goblin in the hut ([G59,63]), accept "[QA1093 Super Reaper 6000]".
08) Do "[QC1062 Goblin Invaders]", "[QC1093 Super Reaper 6000]" and finish up "[QC1069 Deepmoss Spider Eggs]" and "[QC6461 Blood Feeders]" around Windshear Crag: kill the Venture Co. Loggers, kill/loot the Venture Co. Operators until the Blueprints drop (its a low drop rate).\\Also loot the Deepmoss Eggs and kill Deepmoss Venomspitters.\\NOTES: There are a lot of operators on the big tank shredder, ([G63,54]) and more around other structures in the area. 
09) There is a goblin merchant to the west in Windshear Crag ([G58,52]) that you can get repaired/resupplied at.
10) Go back to the goblin in the hut and turn in "[QT1093 Super Reaper 6000]" ([G59,63]), accept "[QA1094 Further Instructions]".
11) Run to Sun Rock Retreat and at the tauren next to the Inn turn in "[QT6284 Arachnophobia]" ([G47,61]).
12) Just north of you at the female tauren, turn in (if you have it) "[QT6401 Kaya's Alive]" ([G47,58]). Also accept "[QA6301 Cycle of Rebirth]".
13) West in the village, get the FP from the Wind Rider Master ([G45,60]). Then next to you from the Bowyer under the red tent, make sure you are repaired/resupplied.[R]
14) Run up the little pathway SW in Sun Rock Retreat, make a left and then accept "[QA6421 Boulderslide Ravine]" and "[QA6562 Trouble in the Deeps]" ([G47,64]).
15) Go SE to Boulderslide Cavern (entrance at [G61,93]) and do "[QC6421 Boulderslide Ravine]": loot the Resonite Crystals in the cave and go far back into the cave towards the water for the Investigation.
16) Go east to the small village of Malaka'Jin and turn in "[QT6461 Blood Feeders]" ([G71,95]). You can get resupplied in the village.[R]
17) Run east and turn in "[QT1062 Goblin Invaders]" (at [G35,28] in the Barrens). Accept "[QA1068 Shredding Machines]".
18) Grind your way up NE and turn in "[QT3921 Wenikee Boltbucket]" ([G49,11]), SKIP "Nugget Slugs".
19) Go north a bit and turn in "[QT6541 Report to Kadrak]" (up in the watchtower, [G48,5]), \\SKIP "The Warsong Reports".\\
[NX 21-21 Ashenvale]
]], "Thacen")
